reviewText: I thought  the cover was fooling me.  After all, what would a nubile, pretty young dancer want with a pudgy middle aged man?  I figured the usual young Bollywood hunk would show up at some point.  He never did.  We are supposed to believe that these two are a hot item.  The acting was actually pretty good but I had to suspend belief too much for this movie to really be enjoyable for me.
